{"ts":"2026-06-26T00:16:14.997Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"submit_and_exit","toolCallId":"zrpn4m4s","input":{"summary":"Audited and verified all forms and interactive tools to ensure they are strictly frontend-only placeholders.\n\nKey steps taken:\n1. Audited the Contact form in `components/ContactSection.tsx`. Modified the submit handler (`handleContactSubmit`) to use a simulated 1-second timeout network delay instead of a real API fetch call to `/api/contact`. Updated the success notification message to clearly state: 'This contact form is currently operating as a premium frontend-only simulation. Backend/FastAPI integration will come later. No real email or data was sent.'\n2. Audited the Newsletter subscribe form in `components/Footer.tsx`. Modified the submission confirmation message to state: '✓ Subscription simulated. (FastAPI integration coming soon)'.\n3. Audited the AI Readiness Assessor in `app/build/assessment/page.tsx`. Added state indicators and handler (`handleDownload`) to replace the static 'Download Custom Advisory PDF' button with an interactive, simulated loading indicator that informs users: 'FastAPI PDF generator integration will come later.'\n4. Audited all other interactive tools including:\n   - Portal login (`app/portal/page.tsx` and `components/inner-pages/SecurePortalPreview.tsx`): Completely client-side toggle status mechanism.\n   - Control Center (`components/CommandCenter.tsx`): Entirely frontend keyboard-driven navigation.\n   - Talk to Agent (`app/build/talk/page.tsx`): Local console chat supervisor simulations.\n   - Blueprint Generator (`components/sections/BlueprintGenerator.tsx`): Multi-step wizard with local suggester codes and client-side compilation triggers.\n   - Operational ROI Calculator (`app/build/roi/page.tsx`): Slider variables computed on the fly on the client side.\n   - Sandbox Simulation Enclave (`app/build/sandbox/page.tsx`): Local trace simulation loop using static log arrays.\n   - Visual Foundry Studio (`app/platforms/foundry/page.tsx`): Dynamic DAG visual state simulator.\n   - Assets Registry Marketplace (`app/platforms/marketplace/page.tsx`): Local state deploying logic.\n5. Successfully ran grep/searches for terms like `fetch`, `axios`, `/api/`, `Cognito`, `SES`, `S3`, `AWS`, `localhost`, and `NEXT_PUBLIC_API` to confirm that no other active or unsafe backend integrations remain.\n6. Ran the test suite via `npm run lint` and `npm run build`, verifying that everything is fully typed, clean, and compiles flawlessly for deployment.","verified":true}}}
